fc_test.x: Use iso_c_bindings module to pass data between Fortran and C codes.

fc2_test.x: Use standard methods to convert between Fortran and C codes. These
are compiler dependent and features like the number of underscores needed in the
C routines may need to be modified depending on the compiler.

f_from_c.x: Demonstrate how to call a Fortran subroutine from C
